cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV. 

The paper discusses machine learning systems that can learn to perform a wider variety of inter-related tasks in more complex environments, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), or computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). However, given the focus on never-ending learning and the development of a testbed for this purpose, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories.
